  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>Restaurant Belvedere</strong> serves traditional Neapolitan cuisine in an elegant dining room that overlooks the sea.</p>
<p><strong>Grill Restaurant &amp; Snack Bar</strong> is open during the day for drinks, snacks and light lunches.</p>
<p><strong>The Bar</strong> offers a large menu of local and international drinks that can be enjoyed on the sea view terrace.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool &amp; Beach</strong></span></p>
<p>A peaceful swimming pool is set amongst the hotels gardens with sun loungers, umbrellas and pool towels available for guests. The pool is normally open from 01 April to 31 October (weather dependent). A lift links the hotel directly to the sea below where a bathing platform is open from 01 Jun - 30 Oct and provides sun loungers (payable locally). </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Free wifi</li>
<li>Parking (payable locally, approx. €15 per day)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
