  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double Rooms</strong> enjoy a garden view and a traditional style. They can sleep up to three adults with a third bed available for a supplement. Facilities include air conditioning (Jun-Sep), free wifi, TV, minibar, safe and hairdryer. Some rooms have a french balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Sea View Rooms</strong> enjoy uninterrupted sea views from their French balcony and large windows. They can sleep up to three adults.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> face the sea and offer ample space with stylish furnishings. They sleep up to two people.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
